<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2609406>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Conchoecia rudyakovi Chavtur, sp. nov. (Adult male: A—MIMB 18344/9; B, E, and G—MIMB 18344/14; C— MIMB 18344/2; D—MIMB 18344/6; F—MIMB 18344/7. Adult female: H—MIMB 18344/12; I, L, and M—MIMB 18344/ 10; J—MIMB 18344/19; K—MIMB 18344/18; N—MIMB 18344/11). A—sixth limb; B—proximal part of sixth limb; Dseventh limb; E and F—copulatory appendage; G—distal part of copulatory appendage; H–K—right valve of carapace in lateral view; L and M—carapace in ventral view; N—carapace in posterior view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2609406/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2609414>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Conchoecia angustipilata Chavtur, sp. nov. (Adult male: A–K—MIMB 18346/1). A and B—distal part of endopodite on right and left second antenna; D—mandible (setae not shown); D and E—epipodite of mandible; F—tooth edge of basale endite; G—distal part of maxilla; H—fifth limb; I—sixth limb; J—proximal part of sixth limb; K—furcal appendage." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2609414/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2609430>
    dc:description "FIGURE 18. Conchoecia sculpta Chavtur, sp. nov. (Adult female: A and K—MIMB 18345/4. Adult male: B, H, and I— MIMB 18345/1; C–G, J, L, and M—MIMB 18345/2). A—epipodite of mandible; B—tooth of basale endite; C and D—fifth limb; E—coxale and precoxale of fifth limb; F—sixth limb; G and H—proximal part of sixth limb; I and J—seventh limb; Kdistal part of seventh limb; L—copulatory appendage; M—distal part of copulatory appendage." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2609430/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

